  "title": "Retail Assistant (Part Time)",
  "description": "<p>Full/Part Time Retail Assistant (Cheers convenience store)<br /></p><p>Responsible for stacking, displaying and replenishment of products on the shelves, as well as monitoring expiry dates and shelf lives of products.</p><p>To assist in the loading and unloading of goods, maintain neat and systematic storing of products.</p><p>Perform daily housekeeping.</p><p>Perform cashiering duties.</p><p>Other duties as assigned (if any)<br /></p><p>Requirements:</p><p>Above minimum legal age of 21 years old for handling the sale and supply of tobacco and alcohol products.</p><p>Willing to work on weekends and public holidays.</p><p><br /></p><p>Work Shift Timings:</p><p></p><p>Afternoon: 1500 to 2300hrs (1 hr break/ OT)<br />Work Days: Monday(depending on availability), Tuesday, Wednesday, Thursday </p><p>Salary:</p><p>$10.50/Hr<br /></p><p>Location:</p><p>Rochor Station</p>",
